attributes.review: I am highly disappointed with this app. I downloaded it so i can stay updated with y’all president, trumpet. 🎺🍊After a couple minutes of having it the app started glitching! I started hearing weird macaroni noises as soon as one of his pictures popped up. Unfortunately i had to delete it due to these weird issues. I put my phone down for about 4-5 minutes to go get myself a caprisun and some chips. I came back and went on my phone and the app was right there after I had deleted it ! I opened it and there he was with his silly corn hair🌽 I deleted it again and went on youtube to get my mind off things; but all of a sudden an ad pops up and you will not believe who it was ! it was an ad about trumpet 🎺😞I was beyond scared at this point every app I would go on i’d either see or hear him, I totally do not recommend please stay safe I believe this app can possibly hack your phone and go through your photos and data stay safe guys !🙏🏽
